            <div class="process-step__number">1</div>
            <div class="process-step__content">
              <h3 class="process-step__title">AI Readiness Assessment</h3>
              <p class="process-step__description">
                Evaluate your current processes, data quality, and infrastructure to identify the best AI opportunities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step__number">2</div>
            <div class="process-step__content">
              <h3 class="process-step__title">Solution Design & Planning</h3>
              <p class="process-step__description">
                Design custom AI solutions tailored to your specific needs, with clear ROI projections and implementation timelines.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step__number">3</div>
            <div class="process-step__content">
              <h3 class="process-step__title">Development & Training</h3>
